WEBVTT

00:07:28.364 --> 00:07:32.436
And we also have the relationships
with the governments

00:07:32.460 --> 00:07:36.362
so that we can make sure
that our program is coordinated

00:07:36.386 --> 00:07:38.673
with other disease-control programs,

00:07:38.697 --> 00:07:40.564
so that we can be efficient.

00:07:41.449 --> 00:07:45.680
Wouldn't it be amazing
if we could do this?

00:07:45.704 --> 00:07:47.958
We'd have trachoma on the run.

00:07:47.982 --> 00:07:50.317
We would be on the home straight

00:07:50.341 --> 00:07:53.715
to eliminate this disease
from the whole world.

00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:57.713
But before I finish,
I just want to share with you

00:07:57.737 --> 00:08:00.240
some words from
the founder of Sightsavers,